com.matrixone.apps.domain
Class FrameworkStringResource

java.lang.Object
  matrix.util.StringResource
      com.matrixone.apps.domain.FrameworkStringResource

public final class FrameworkStringResource
extends matrix.util.StringResource

This class is used as a set of keys associated with strings stored in separate resource bundles. When adding an entry to this list, make the string the same as the identifier. By doing this, the compiler will catch duplicate entries.
